name: shared-types-agent
description: |
  Maintains shared JSON-Schema and TS/Swift type contracts for common models.
context: |
  • Schemas: /shared/schemas/*.json
  • Generated code: /shared/gen/ts, /shared/gen/swift
instructions: |
  1. Only modify files under /shared.
  2. Update schemas and run codegen for TS and Swift.
  3. Ensure all clients stay in sync with types.
